<title>HONG KONG: BZW sets call warrants on red-chip basket.</title>
<headline>BZW sets call warrants on red-chip basket.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1997-04-25</dateline>
<text>
<p>BZW Warrants Ltd said on Friday it has launched 200 million American-style call warrants on shares of a basket of seven red-chip stocks.</p>
<p>Each basket comprises:</p>
<p> China Everbright-IHD Pacific Ltd	     0.3 shrs</p>
<p> Beijing Datang Power Generation Co Ltd     0.5 shrs</p>
<p> China Merchant Hai Hong Holdings Ltd	 0.3 shrs</p>
<p> China Aerospace International Holdings Ltd 0.8 shrs</p>
<p> CNPC (Hong Kong) Ltd			     2.4 shrs</p>
<p> Shenyin Wanguo (H.K.) Ltd			0.8 shrs</p>
<p> China Resources Enterprise Ltd		 0.1 shrs</p>
<p>Ten warrants control one basket.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE	 HK$16.385	 PREMIUM	 19.32 PCT</p>
<p> ISSUE PRICE	  HK$0.3165	 GEARING	 5.18x</p>
<p> EXPIRATION	   23.JAN.98	 MIN EXER LOT  10,000</p>
<p> REFERENCE SPOT     HK$16.3845</p>
<p> LISTING		LUXEMBOURG</p>
<p> NOTE		   PHYSICAL DELIVERY OR CASH SETTLEMENT ON</p>
<p>			  ISSUER'S DISCRETION</p>
<p>-- Hong Kong newsroom (852) 2843 6370</p>
</text>
